                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9348" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0361</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">942 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">相机而动，扭转乾坤：正源水产生产运营流程的蜕变与转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Watch for an Opportunity, Retrieve a Situation: Change and Transformation of the Production and Operation Process of Aquatic Technology Development Co., Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">裴学亮，许翊堃，李晓强，王艳珍，郑智勇，陈铃，孟庆丰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华侨大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">正源水产科技开发有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营流程；运营目标；流程再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Operational Process, Operational Goals, Process Reengineering</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了正源水产科技开发有限公司（以下简称正源水产）以泰国食品展上获得的俄罗斯外贸订单为契机，根据公司经营目标的变化，对生产运营流程进行转型的过程。面对外贸订单的高风险、高不确定性特点，正源水产通过客户订单流程分析，对其关键流程关节进行变革，确保订单安全顺利完成；为了解决市场需求持续增长、原材料不稳定、企业季节性运营、生产能力不足等问题，正源水产运用机械化赋能、灵活化用工等方法，对生产加工流程实施转型，实现了产能持续增长、员工留存率高的企业可持续发展运营目标；针对企业原材料供应不稳定、订单不可持续的困境，通过多元化采购、智能化仓储对物料仓储流程进行再造，达成稳定、高效的库存管理目标。本案例旨在引导学生探讨企业面对内外部环境及运营目标的变化，如何灵活变革生产运营流程实现高质量发展，进一步地理论结合实际掌握运营目标、生产运营流程、流程再造等相关知识点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the transformation process of production and operation process of Zhengyuan Aquatic Technology Development Co., Ltd (hereinafter referred to as Zhengyuan Aquatic) according to the change of the company&#39;s business objectives by taking the opportunity of the foreign trade order from Russia, which was obtained from the Thailand Food Exhibition. In the face of the high-risk and high uncertainty characteristics of foreign trade orders, Zhengyuan Aquatic conducts order process analysis to reform its key process joints and ensure the safe and smooth completion of orders; In order to solve the problems of sustained market demand growth, unstable raw materials, seasonal operation of enterprises, and insufficient production capacity, Zhengyuan Aquatic uses methods such as mechanization empowerment and flexible employment to transform the production and processing processes, achieving the sustainable development and operation goals of continuous capacity growth and high employee retention rate; In response to the difficulties of unstable raw material supply and unsustainable orders, the material warehousing process is restructured through diversified procurement and intelligent warehousing to achieve stable and efficient warehousing management goals. This case aims to guide students to explore how enterprises can flexibly transform their operational processes to achieve high-quality development in the face of changes in internal and external environments and operational goals, and further combine theory with practice to master relevant knowledge points such as operational goals, operational processes, and process reengineering.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《生产运营管理》、《组织管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">运营目标；生产运营流程分析；组织变革的过程</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
